                        <p>Facilities Management</p>
<p>Acacia is a privately owned Supplier Independent Facilities Management &amp; Facilities Consultancy Company operating across Ireland, the UK and the Middle East.</p>
<p>Acacia work in partnership with our clients and provide them with expert advice and support on all facilities and property related matters. We have a proven track record in achieving savings through innovative solutions, operational efficiencies and the use of best practice. We focus on our clients non-core services so that they can focus on their core business.</p>
<p>Acacia provide the following core services:</p>
<p>&#8211; Facilities Management Service<br />
